author_ssm: David Brown in 2010 with additional notes written by Andrea Kutsenkow in 2016.
abstract_ssm: This collection is comprised of materials documenting Jerry G. Dickason's and Elly Dickason's affiliation with the Judson Memorial Church and its associated organizations, including materials related to the production of the book Remembering Judson House, which was published in 2000. These materials date between 1920 and 2012 and include correspondence, manuscripts, research notes, research materials, galley proofs, board minutes, photographs, newspaper clippings, transcripts of sermons, church bulletins, artwork, and media.
